  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Embrace art of the Alchemy!</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is a <strong>classic puzzle in the \"alchemy\" genre!</strong> At the beginning, you have <strong>only four basic elements,</strong> but over time <strong>your mastery will grow,</strong> and you will gain access to more <strong>complex recipes!</strong> An exciting adventure awaits you in the world of alchemical combinations! <strong>Discover over 1000 different elements!</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549700/extras/2317f990e7e398eed3633cf2453151a5.poster.avif?t=1768156265\" width=800 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549700/extras/2317f990e7e398eed3633cf2453151a5.webm?t=1768156265\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549700/extras/2317f990e7e398eed3633cf2453151a5.mp4?t=1768156265\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unique setting</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The game</strong> takes place in a <i><strong>fantasy post-apocalyptic world</strong></i> on the brink of extinction due <strong>to a global cataclysm.</strong> With each completed quest, <strong>you will discover new corners</strong> of this world that can <strong>tell a story about its past.</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549700/extras/35f2c7107013e14ae171782c29968aab.poster.avif?t=1768156265\" width=800 height=595 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549700/extras/35f2c7107013e14ae171782c29968aab.webm?t=1768156265\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Meet the local inhabitants</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>On your path to learning alchemy,</strong> you will meet <strong>fabulous creatures: elves, dragons, dwarves, Valkyries... spiders?!</strong> Each of them has its own story, which you can learn if you are <strong>curious enough!</strong> Chat with the <strong>characters to learn more</strong> about the incredible <strong>world of Fusion!</strong></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549700/extras/d2ba4d3ee851483875a7e22b781afdfe.poster.avif?t=1768156265\" width=800 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549700/extras/d2ba4d3ee851483875a7e22b781afdfe.webm?t=1768156265\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549700/extras/d2ba4d3ee851483875a7e22b781afdfe.mp4?t=1768156265\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Gameplay Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>In addition</strong> to the <strong>main gameplay</strong> and <strong>chatting with characters,</strong> you <strong>have access to many mini-games</strong> that open up as you <strong>progress through the story: visit a bar, fight chimeras, brew tea, grow plants</strong>... and, of course, click on the cookie! <strong><i>click-click-click!!!</i></strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549700/extras/e8d8d86e85481717c98c609cadd291c5.avif?t=1768156265\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549700/extras_big/e8d8d86e85481717c98c609cadd291c5.avif?t=1768156265 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Embrace art of the Alchemy!</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is a <strong>classic puzzle in the \"alchemy\" genre!</strong> At the beginning, you have <strong>only four basic elements,</strong> but over time <strong>your mastery will grow,</strong> and you will gain access to more <strong>complex recipes!</strong> An exciting adventure awaits you in the world of alchemical combinations! <strong>Discover over 1000 different elements!</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549700/extras/2317f990e7e398eed3633cf2453151a5.poster.avif?t=1768156265\" width=800 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549700/extras/2317f990e7e398eed3633cf2453151a5.webm?t=1768156265\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549700/extras/2317f990e7e398eed3633cf2453151a5.mp4?t=1768156265\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unique setting</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The game</strong> takes place in a <i><strong>fantasy post-apocalyptic world</strong></i> on the brink of extinction due <strong>to a global cataclysm.</strong> With each completed quest, <strong>you will discover new corners</strong> of this world that can <strong>tell a story about its past.</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549700/extras/35f2c7107013e14ae171782c29968aab.poster.avif?t=1768156265\" width=800 height=595 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549700/extras/35f2c7107013e14ae171782c29968aab.webm?t=1768156265\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Meet the local inhabitants</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>On your path to learning alchemy,</strong> you will meet <strong>fabulous creatures: elves, dragons, dwarves, Valkyries... spiders?!</strong> Each of them has its own story, which you can learn if you are <strong>curious enough!</strong> Chat with the <strong>characters to learn more</strong> about the incredible <strong>world of Fusion!</strong></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549700/extras/d2ba4d3ee851483875a7e22b781afdfe.poster.avif?t=1768156265\" width=800 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549700/extras/d2ba4d3ee851483875a7e22b781afdfe.webm?t=1768156265\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549700/extras/d2ba4d3ee851483875a7e22b781afdfe.mp4?t=1768156265\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Gameplay Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>In addition</strong> to the <strong>main gameplay</strong> and <strong>chatting with characters,</strong> you <strong>have access to many mini-games</strong> that open up as you <strong>progress through the story: visit a bar, fight chimeras, brew tea, grow plants</strong>... and, of course, click on the cookie! <strong><i>click-click-click!!!</i></strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549700/extras/e8d8d86e85481717c98c609cadd291c5.avif?t=1768156265\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps